name: Pair_zipTest
description: Unit tests for the Pair.zip method, which zips two lists into a list of pairs.

test_cases.name: testZipStrictEqualSize
test_cases.description: Tests the Pair.zip method with two lists of equal size and strict mode enabled.

test_cases.name: testZipStrictDifferentSize
test_cases.description: Tests the Pair.zip method with two lists of different sizes and strict mode enabled, expecting an AssertionError.

test_cases.name: testZipNonStrict
test_cases.description: Tests the Pair.zip method with two lists of different sizes and strict mode disabled.
